{"tid":2212251,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你告訴我一個 昆德拉的故事","createTime":"2020-09-21T15:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T12:51:53.000Z","uid":60658,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d523d2d206f513cf31f0629dc6b7ce337f1ed518","tid":2212251,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832ce6fbe8b1720acfae165b859005a4423557d2","tid":2212251,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:53:18.000Z","msg":"羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f430062e997e33a92629179e5e9c52a28624cd","tid":2212251,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"1929年愚人節，米蘭．昆德拉（Milan Kundera）在捷克斯洛伐克出生，但我們很少會把他定義為捷克作家。一般來說，對昆德拉的定義是「法國作家」，抑或是「以捷克語書寫的法國作家」、「流亡作家」，激進一點的甚至會把他定義為法國人。這類定義有一定歷史因素，原因是昆德拉的作品因蘇聯共產黨的原故，在故鄉捷克長期被禁，而他本人在1975年在巴黎定居，很長一段時間也沒有回到故鄉去。他的作品通常都直接在法國出版，包括我們常見的《生命中不能承受之輕》。"},{"pid":"6ee3b8b09e8e2f77bc051d2097ac8e71866b582a","tid":2212251,"uid":301668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"milan<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea42da8d8d80b95f62dd51fc9fcaea71e942657","tid":2212251,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:56:38.000Z","msg":"Mla"},{"pid":"7defe09a5d04417b57870511bd5e7ee4ab552836","tid":2212251,"uid":82359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:58:10.000Z","msg":"關於一對情侶，假裝陌生男女"},{"pid":"a7db9113c0d5b5867fda121a4889eda79b8e86d6","tid":2212251,"uid":5700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1282bfde3ce363266681483a0ea15662794ef3","tid":2212251,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"832ce6